## 4. Destructuring

Used constantly in route handlers and React components.

```javascript
// Object destructuring
const { url_name, platinum, quantity } = order;
// same as:
const url_name = order.url_name;
const platinum = order.platinum;

// Array destructuring
const [first, second] = prices;

// In function parameters
function handleOrder({ url_name, platinum }) {
  console.log(url_name, platinum);
}

// With defaults
const { rank = 0, maxRank = 5 } = order;
```

