## 11. Common traps summary

| Trap | Solution |
|---|---|
| Forgot `await` → gets `Promise` instead of data | Add `await` before every async call |
| `sort()` without comparator → sorts as strings | Always use `.sort((a,b) => a-b)` |
| `\|\|` instead of `??` → treats 0 as falsy | Use `??` when 0 is a valid value |
| No `try/catch` → app crashes on network error | Wrap all fetch/DB calls |
| Mutating state directly → React doesn't re-render | Always use `setState(...)`, never `state.push(...)` |
| No `res.json()` in Express route → browser hangs | Every route must send a response |
| Adding function to useEffect deps → infinite loop | Move function outside or use useCallback |
| better-sqlite3 with `await` → doesn't work | It's synchronous — no await needed |

